data.description:
Welcome to this updated 3 bed, 2 bath ranch home located near schools, shopping and parks. This home has 
a large lot, oversize driveway, and great patio/backyard for grilling and enjoying company outside. As you 
walk in to the property notice the gorgeous hardwood floors, the unique ceiling seams, wood burning 
fireplace and the beautiful light. The beautiful updated kitchen with stainless steel 
appliances does not disappoint and plenty of counter space. Spacious bedrooms. Main floor laundry. This 
home is one you do not want to miss!
